{"tid":1244202,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"重新安裝line但登入唔到","createTime":"2019-06-19T20:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T06:02:39.000Z","uid":265553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57a2af6d09bdde8e30c5d5e308c470a589498665","tid":1244202,"uid":265553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T20:22:03.000Z","msg":"發生咗好大問題所以特登開個連登account 問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個line 不嬲淨係連接facebook, 冇連電話同email,  尋日line 壞壞地諗住delete line個app重裝。點知佢就不斷話我舊手機要揀「移動帳號設定」同埋「傳送移動帳號認證碼」。<br />\n<br />\n咁我又唔係換電話，根本開唔到「舊」電話個account 設定同收個認證碼，一路卡住咗喺度。Email咗Line個客戶服務但話要兩三日先覆。<br />\n<br />\n本身line同人傾緊計同約咗人 (冇其他聯絡方法)，搞到尋晚已經放咗人一次飛機。睇吓大家有冇試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bce869069ba3942c7101d120fd18a09533a6dee","tid":1244202,"uid":5574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T20:24:44.000Z","msg":"無...<br />\n開個新account...<br />\ndelete 之前唔睇下"},{"pid":"7e53fa0e67b12cb47db0a4049843ba8e7ad98bea","tid":1244202,"uid":265553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bce869069ba3942c7101d120fd18a09533a6dee","tid":1244202,"uid":5574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T20:24:44.000Z","msg":"無...<br />\n開個新account...<br />\ndelete 之前唔睇下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T20:26:48.000Z","msg":"咁嚴重，之前啲對話唔緊要，但friend list ......"},{"pid":"ddd7e01648151662cbe18f9494d6dc9ab3285a59","tid":1244202,"uid":37502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T22:45:24.000Z","msg":"重裝前有冇用其他device login咗先？(e.g. PC, iPad)<br />\n至少可以拎到個code先。"},{"pid":"803a6ad83d39217037977ffdc3f12c3faf43d7ce","tid":1244202,"uid":265553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd7e01648151662cbe18f9494d6dc9ab3285a59","tid":1244202,"uid":37502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite